  },
  "pronunciation_dictionary_locators": [
    {
      "pronunciation_dictionary_id": "AhK3J8mZDRoShxfoJLk6",
      "version_id": "pFvyQBbxEBKyF7C3IHpy"
    }
  ],
  "inter_chunk_silence_ms": 650,
  "chunks": [
    {
      "index": 0,
      "text": "Anthropic just opened the gates. Third-party Claude agents that were banned from your subscription \u2014 OpenClaw, and others like it \u2014 can now authenticate through your plan starting June 15.",
      "checksum": "sha256:61bcda3d65037026d435738382913c89f08280dccd7728262ec05b0366729566",
      "wav": "chunk-00.wav",
      "duration": 10.7740589569161,
      "word_count": 30,
      "words_offset": 0
    },
    {
      "index": 1,
      "text": "And Anthropic added a new credit pool to pay for them.",
      "checksum": "sha256:b7ec32cef51909ec752d2f229618d270ff4d6a3837bd20b6c3b2312e7a7a0b1b",
      "wav": "chunk-01.wav",
      "duration": 2.8328344671201813,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 30
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "text": "Most builders haven't noticed yet. Here's what was true until June 15.",
      "checksum": "sha256:08d9fb27975a2097b309a1ab08538da7f43b96406f424cc8b23c74b49318666b",
      "wav": "chunk-02.wav",
      "duration": 4.783310657596372,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 41
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "text": "Third-party autonomous agents like OpenClaw weren't allowed to authenticate through your Claude subscription.",
      "checksum": "sha256:c5140c47f19d11e2db19af1b7a5b11144391ca64b1a3bed1f27574424235e3c4",
      "wav": "chunk-03.wav",
      "duration": 5.897868480725624,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 53
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "text": "Separate API setup. Separately billed. Dev harnesses like Archon \u2014 which just wrap your Claude Code workflow \u2014 sat in a gray zone.",
      "checksum": "sha256:a0c703252d31cedb4b5c8454c84a5a720ee0e4f43add7c987c24a306593409a1",
      "wav": "chunk-04.wav",
      "duration": 8.17342403628118,
      "word_count": 23,
      "words_offset": 66
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "text": "And your own Agent SDK scripts? Those counted against the same usage limit as your editor work.",
      "checksum": "sha256:52ca131271d4163adc1284e58712bcb07910fba9e556a7a3f934391cb75fd4f9",
      "wav": "chunk-05.wav",
      "duration": 5.712108843537415,
      "word_count": 17,
      "words_offset": 89
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "text": "Starting June 15, Anthropic clears the rules.",
      "checksum": "sha256:ea6578092a8c3cbf05ad4f508497b7da3e94d122765ad334cc48a5dd43613ad8",
      "wav": "chunk-06.wav",
      "duration": 2.7399546485260773,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 106
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "text": "A new monthly programmatic credit lands on every paid plan, separate from your editor budget.",
      "checksum": "sha256:e5043fdc1f0943deea723bac9d35096006fbcae17cafd1393815a33525dd89ef",
      "wav": "chunk-07.wav",
      "duration": 5.108390022675737,
      "word_count": 15,
      "words_offset": 113
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "text": "And third-party Agent SDK tools \u2014 including the previously-banned ones \u2014 can now officially authenticate through your Claude plan and draw from this credit pool.",
      "checksum": "sha256:6430c66d544bb9bb3f32d6a6ab776f447fbcb7b80052999598adb315a950c7d7",
      "wav": "chunk-08.wav",
      "duration": 10.170340136054422,
      "word_count": 25,
      "words_offset": 128
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "text": "Here's the math. Pro: twenty bucks. Max five-x: a hundred. Max twenty-x: two hundred. Team and Enterprise included. Free plan?",
      "checksum": "sha256:3e95344677833e94663d9c9365593867b8dd378cbfd890426ed084d027921b0b",
      "wav": "chunk-09.wav",
      "duration": 11.23845804988662,
      "word_count": 20,
      "words_offset": 153
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "text": "Zero. Not invited.\n\nHere's the rollout. Today: nothing changes.",
      "checksum": "sha256:fa025d94fc5a94c6d087adf1c721cf076fb6d140e052434893aeefe7b5103a3e",
      "wav": "chunk-10.wav",
      "duration": 3.9938321995464854,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 173
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "text": "June 8: every paid user gets an email with the claim link.",
      "checksum": "sha256:91635f91affd5c646941b0495cd32cb24bd5d8801a4c756a5bd2bd904bc1f2f0",
      "wav": "chunk-11.wav",
      "duration": 3.7616326530612243,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 182
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "text": "June 15: the new programmatic credit goes into effect.",
      "checksum": "sha256:fbd96f49f71274f0481c006bbddf82f108a86997a4fa54296be70b1b2d3e9bc8",
      "wav": "chunk-12.wav",
      "duration": 3.6687528344671203,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 194
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "text": "Across every Agent SDK surface. But there's a catch.",
      "checksum": "sha256:814e9437373bf394c557ffb91e2450b26b6913602264b1a0ffd7d2758e364297",
      "wav": "chunk-13.wav",
      "duration": 3.3901133786848074,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 203
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "text": "The cap is small. Twenty bucks on Pro burns in a few hundred Agent SDK calls.",
      "checksum": "sha256:b7eafb2b3682b28f4ff83e4cfc7ec6883386b9997a9f5b497b4da994637d361a",
      "wav": "chunk-14.wav",
      "duration": 4.73687074829932,
      "word_count": 16,
      "words_offset": 212
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "text": "Hit the ceiling \u2014 and one of two things happens.",
      "checksum": "sha256:125b10541ab9b914d4997057a06a66456edb3c726203a45805e2a864ab27a233",
      "wav": "chunk-15.wav",
      "duration": 2.693514739229025,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 228
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "text": "Extra usage on, you flow to standard API rates per token.",
      "checksum": "sha256:62492de4911a12c03b8ec9e50ceba28bb4336706565990f7bcd803969f027f0b",
      "wav": "chunk-16.wav",
      "duration": 3.297233560090703,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 238
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "text": "Extra usage off, every SDK request hard-stops until next month.",
      "checksum": "sha256:e1fb894ede98557981f26d4615e8dcae32575d0b69fc639cecbfa789fe9568ef",
      "wav": "chunk-17.wav",
      "duration": 3.6687528344671203,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 249
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "text": "There's no middle ground. Builders are split.",
      "checksum": "sha256:db53ea3b96239e2d0516d63e6ae9508f849379873fc0df3af591c41824de72f1",
      "wav": "chunk-18.wav",
      "duration": 2.182675736961451,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 259
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "text": "Some are stoked \u2014 third-party agents are finally allowed on the plan, no more juggling separate API keys.",
      "checksum": "sha256:881dfaec9da8883df4d631839ce7e35941df9df38cd9e45fd04115d97d48754a",
      "wav": "chunk-19.wav",
      "duration": 6.455147392290249,
      "word_count": 18,
      "words_offset": 266
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "text": "Some are skeptical \u2014 twenty bucks on Pro won't last builders running real Agent SDK loops.",
      "checksum": "sha256:9667cf0baaff22cc53840039e915aeb859d4ed16c89b1d523b5825f5ec3b643f",
      "wav": "chunk-20.wav",
      "duration": 5.38702947845805,
      "word_count": 16,
      "words_offset": 284
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "text": "And some are confused \u2014 what counts as programmatic versus interactive?",
      "checksum": "sha256:fa39ce25d5965d13af0208219ed3741b4459221125277a1c4004e2ee10380104",
      "wav": "chunk-21.wav",
      "duration": 4.690430839002268,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 300
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "text": "The line isn't clear. Net upside for most builders.",
      "checksum": "sha256:c0cc4bca732159e547234232fc29584ca3d4007b4aec533279950dbee5c6cd3a",
      "wav": "chunk-22.wav",
      "duration": 2.9257142857142857,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 311
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "text": "Two budgets instead of one. Programmatic gets its own pool.",
      "checksum": "sha256:b48ae17df739955de8c278adbdeff594d8e3069ea09858e39a8a3366001dab95",
      "wav": "chunk-23.wav",
      "duration": 3.4829931972789114,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 320
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "text": "Your editor work stays protected. The only real question \u2014 is that ceiling tall enough for what you actually run?",
      "checksum": "sha256:5e40a481cf272c53a40e8652bfb72e10ca212c2cbc3fd40e85ab1f8e54b6f615",
      "wav": "chunk-24.wav",
      "duration": 6.826666666666667,
      "word_count": 20,
      "words_offset": 330
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "text": "Twenty bucks of programmatic credit on Pro \u2014 generous Anthropic move, or just enough rope to hang yourself?",
      "checksum": "sha256:5c0475b32d6ffa4968453fe45f610185cab4036f68c0d7583da07ce377ecbb5b",
      "wav": "chunk-25.wav",
      "duration": 6.548027210884354,
      "word_count": 18,
      "words_offset": 350
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "text": "Drop your pick below.",
      "checksum": "sha256:af22c78ddf829f074e3d1149b006a8f74f5c36033481d9a5c7b43881fc9f8264",
      "wav": "chunk-26.wav",
      "duration": 1.207437641723356,
      "word_count": 4,
      "words_offset": 368
    }
  ]
}